One of the things about being a cruise ship captain is that some of the job's duties have nothing to do with actually driving the ship.  Here, Captain Rob Hempstead (nearest to camera) is taking part in a quick-fire cake decorating competition with some of the crew and passengers on board the Rhapsody of the Seas.
